					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The output file will still be 32k PRG if all you did was change the header. I believe most emulators would read the header and load the first 16KB PRG chunk only into $C000 (mirrored to $8000), which means all the vectors point to $0000 or whatever your fill value for ROM is.</div>

